data.description: Beautiful Townhome in the very popular community of Plantation Lakes.  This home offers a one car garage; two bedrooms each with its own private full bath and additional half bath on ground level. Owner recently installed new luxury plank vinal flooring in family room, new central air unit and new ceiling fans in both the living area and Owner's suite. The kitchen and eating area are adjacent to the family room offering a modern open floor plan. The home is located in close walking distance to the pool and clubhouse.  This amenity rich community offers tennis courts, basketball courts, wellness inspired community center, 18 hole championship golf course, the award-winning Landing Bar and Grille, walking trails, outdoor pool and more.  Make this one your new home.  You will not be disappointed!
